{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/2022-08-17-everythin-can-helm-chart/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<!-- vim-markdown-toc GitLab -->\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#helm\">Helm</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#remote-repo\">remote repo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#local-repo\">local repo</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\">小结</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#reference\">Reference</a></li>\n</ul>\n<!-- vim-markdown-toc -->\n<h1 id=\"前言\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"前言 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前言</h1>\n<p>helm 简单介绍</p>\n<h1 id=\"helm\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#helm\" aria-label=\"helm permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Helm</h1>\n<p>helm 作为 k8s 的包管理工具，使用还是非常广的。</p>\n<h2 id=\"remote-repo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#remote-repo\" aria-label=\"remote repo permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>remote repo</h2>\n<p>第三方提供的 helm repo</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>helm repo add devops <a href=\"https://harbor.xxx.cn/chartrepo/xxxx\">https://harbor.xxx.cn/chartrepo/xxxx</a></p>\n<p>添加 repo</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm update</p>\n<p>更新 repo</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm install fdb-operator —version 0.2.0 devops/fdb-operator -n fdb</p>\n<p>安装</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm upgrade fdb-operator —version 0.4.0 devops/fdb-operator -n fdb</p>\n<p>更新</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm uninstall fdb-operator</p>\n<p>卸载</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"local-repo\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#local-repo\" aria-label=\"local repo permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>local repo</h2>\n<p>新建一个 chart</p>\n<ol>\n<li>\n<p>helm create xxxx</p>\n<p>创建一个 xxxx 的 chart</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm lint .</p>\n<p>检查一下有没有报错</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm package .</p>\n<p>打包成 tar.gz 文件</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm install xxxx ./xxxx -n xxxx</p>\n<p>打包前也可以本地安装测试下。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>helm uninstall xxxx</p>\n<p>测试完成可以选择删除</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm plugin install <a href=\"https://github.com/chartmuseum/helm-push\">https://github.com/chartmuseum/helm-push</a></p>\n<p>如果需要推送到 harbor 就需要安装<code class=\"language-text\">helm-push</code>插件</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm repo add —username=xxxx —password=xxxx myrepo <a href=\"https://harbor.xxx.cn/chartrepo/xxxx\">https://harbor.xxx.cn/chartrepo/xxxx</a></p>\n<p>当然推送之前需要添加 repo</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>helm cm-push xxxx-0.2.0.tgz myrepo</p>\n<p>上传到 repo</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"小结\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%B0%8F%E7%BB%93\" aria-label=\"小结 permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>小结</h1>\n<p>这里只是介绍下 helm 的使用，具体怎么写 helm chart 没有涉及，</p>\n<h1 id=\"reference\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#reference\" aria-label=\"reference permalink\" class=\"toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Reference</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://helm.sh/\">https://helm.sh/</a></li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#helm\">Helm</